title: 24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
